comex rais margin for silver futur the commod exchang inc said it is increas the minimum margin for silver futur contract , effect at the open of busi thursday , april 2. the margin for specul trade will be increas to 2,000 dlr per contract from 1,300 dlr and trade hedg margin will rise to 1,400 dlr from 900 dlr , the comex said . margin are unchang for gold , copper , and aluminum contract , it said .